        <ArticleTitle>Hepatic effects of propofol infusion syndrome.</ArticleTitle>
        <Abstract>
          <AbstractText>Propofol infusion syndrome is a rare but life-threatening complication associated with prolonged propofol administration at high doses. We report three cases of hepatic failure following propofol infusion in the ICU setting.</AbstractText>
